---
// Hero: cabecera inmersiva — video de fondo 100vh, estética dark luxury
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="relative h-screen w-full overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center"
  style="background-color: #0A0A0A;"
  aria-label="Cabecera principal RB Ganadería"
>
  <!-- Video — reemplazar con video de drones de la hacienda -->
  <video
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
    src="/placeholder.mp4"
    autoplay muted loop playsinline
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></video>

  <!-- Overlay negro profundo sobre video -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(10,10,10,0.55) 0%, rgba(10,10,10,0.65) 50%, rgba(10,10,10,0.95) 100%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Línea carmesí superior — firma del logo -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px"
    style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #8B1A1A 30%, #8B1A1A 70%, transparent);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Contenido centrado -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto opacity-0 animate-fade-up"
    style="animation-delay: 0.4s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
  >
    <!-- Overline dorado -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-5 mb-8">
      <div class="h-px w-14" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #C9963A);"></div>
      <p class="font-sans text-xs tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-medium" style="color: #C9963A;">
        Colombia · Ganadería de Excelencia
      </p>
      <div class="h-px w-14" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, #C9963A);"></div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-serif leading-tight mb-8" style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5rem); color: #F0EBE1;">
      RB Ganadería:<br/>
      <em style="font-style: italic; color: rgba(240,235,225,0.65);">Elevando el Estándar<br/>del Campo Colombiano</em>
    </h1>

    <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(240,235,225,0.55);">
      Décadas de trayectoria, rigor genético y compromiso inquebrantable con la sostenibilidad productiva de nuestra nación.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Flecha de scroll -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-scroll-arrow">
    <a href="#fundacion" class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group" aria-label="Ver más">
      <span
        class="block w-px h-10 transition-all duration-500"
        style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(201,150,58,0.5));"
      ></span>
      <svg
        class="w-4 h-4 transition-colors duration-300"
        style="color: rgba(201,150,58,0.55);"
        fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
